cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a new learning-to-rank method for cancer drug selection, which involves using drug and cell line latent vectors to predict drug ranking structures. This involves leveraging genomics information on cell lines. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security)
